quran[11]{c,v,t}:
  12,58,"Abasiani babu Yusuf nibetsa, nibenjila ewa Yusuf, naye nabamanya nabo nibalamumanya tawe"
  12,59,"Ne olwa yabakasilia eshiakhulia shiabu, nababoolela mbu “Mungalushile nende Omusiani wenyu khu papa wenyu” Koo, shimulola mbu ebaleng’asilisiye eshichelo, nasi endi omuwani omulayi"
  12,60,"“Ne nimulamurera tawe, shindilibahelesia shiosi shiosi okhurula khwisie tawe, nemulasitakhwo ahambi hano tawe.”"
  12,61,"Nibaboola mbu; “Khwitsa okhutema okhwikweta samwana , ne toto khulakhola khurio.”"
  12,62,"Ne naboolela abakholi baye; “omwandu kwabu mure mumisiko chiabu, khobanyoole\tokhukulola nibakhakalushila Abandu babu, khobanyoole okhukalukha khandi"
  12,63,"Olwa bakalukha khu sabwe, baboola mbu : “ ewe Papa wefu, bakhwikalile eshibaba, kho okhuhelesie omusiani wefu khutsie naye kho khunyoole okhuhebwa eshibaba, ne toto efwe khulamulinda.”"
  12,64,"Naboola mbu:“ndakhabasuulila khu uno shingala ndabasuubila khumusiani wabu khale awo? Ne Nyasaye niye omulindi omulayi, naye ni Owetsimbabaasi umalayo .”"
  12,65,"Ne olwa baboolola emisiko chiabu , nibanyoolamwo emiandu chiabu chikalusibwe, ni baboola mbu: “ewe papa wefu shina shindi shiakhwenya? chino ni emiandu chiefu chikalusibwe khwifwe! khurere eshakhulia khulwa Abandu befu, ne khwitsa okhulinda omusiani wefu, ne khulanyoola eshibaba shie ingamia ndala, esho neshichelo eshititi. (khubuhani bwomwami)"
  12,66,"Naboola mbu:“shindalamulekhula atsie ninanyu tawe okhula shingala muletsuba khulira lia Nyasaye mbu mulachelela ninaye halali nimubotokhanwa mwesi. “ olwa bamuhelesia indakano eyo yaboola mbu “Nyasaye niye omulindi khukakhuboolanga kano.”"
  12,67,"Naboola mbu: “enywe Abaana banje! Mulenjila mwesi mumuliango mulala tawe, injilile mumiliango chikabukhaane. Ne esie shebakhonyakhwo shiosi shiosi imbeli wa Nyasaye tawe. Amakhuwa koosi kali khu Nyasaye. Naye niye wakhwisikanga, ne besikanga bamwisiche butswa Ye"
  12,68,"Ne olwabenjila shingala Sabwe yabebaalila, shishiabakhonyakhwo shiosi shiosi khu Nyasaye tawe halali akali mumwoyo kwa Yaqub kamala kekholeshe. Netoto ye yali wamachesi shichila khwamwechesia, halali Abandu abanji shibamanyile tawe"